io.github.newnc.model

Class MovieRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • io.github.newnc.model.AbstractRepository
        • io.github.newnc.model.MovieRepository

  • public class MovieRepository
extends AbstractRepository
    This class represents an in-memory repository of movies gets from TMDB API. This class implements the singleton pattern.
    See Also:
    Singleton Pattern
